title: [Rambling Meadows, Lower Fields]
description: The black husk of a small tool shed squats amidst the tall grasses, its badly weathered and rotting wall panels leaning against a low rise to the south.  A rhythmic squeaking emanates from a vacant doorway on one side of the ruined shed.

The black husk of a small tool shed squats amidst the tall grasses, its badly weathered and rotting wall panels leaning against a low rise to the south.  Its roof has completely disintegrated, leaving its interior victim to the elements and the unstoppable progress of the meadow grass.  A rhythmic squeaking emanates from a vacant doorway on one side of the ruined shed.
